Description: The Flight into Egypt: crossing a brook; the Virgin and child on a donkey being led towards the right, across a brook by Joseph who is on foot. 1654 Etching, engraving and drypoint with accidental surface tone marks along the lower margin Watermark: Countermark AD (Hinterding catalogue, variant A.a.a.)
Curator's comments: For another (late) impression see 1941,0327.11.48 This print is one of six in similar format depicting scenes from Christ's youth, for comment see F,4.90.
